      "wikitext": "{{Infobox building\n|name      = Well\n|image     = Well.png\n|cost      = {{Price|1000}}\n|materials = {{name|Stone|75}}\n|animals   =\n|upgrade   =\n|size      = 3x3\n|sizehv    = 3x3\n|width     = 100px\n}}\n\nThe '''Well''' is a [[Carpenter's Shop#Farm Buildings|farm building]] purchasable from [[Robin]] at the [[Carpenter's Shop]] that allows the player to refill their [[Watering Cans|Watering Can]].  It takes two days for Robin to complete its construction.\n\n==Behavior==\nInteracting with the well with a watering can equipped will refill it as if the player was next to water.\n\n{{NavboxBuildings}}\n\n[[Category:Farm buildings]]\n\n[[de:Brunnen]]\n[[es:Pozo]]\n[[fr:Puits]]\n[[it:Pozzo]]\n[[ja:井戸]]\n[[ko:우물]]\n[[hu:Kút]]\n[[pt:Poço]]\n[[ru:Колодец]]\n[[tr:Kuyu]]\n[[zh:水井]]"
